description: An opportunity beckons for 1st-time buyers or empty nesters looking to downsize into a spacious one-bedroom, one-bath condo with one deeded parking space and a private patio yard. This unit, constructed in 1988, features a practical galley kitchen and is conveniently located within steps of the Broadway shops and Broadway T station, minutes from the airport and the Seaport/Financial District. Other features include in-unit laundry (full size), an open floor plan, extra storage in a crawl space, and built-in AC units.
